content:
with dripping umbrellas in tow many arrived at Daniels Graduate Hall on Tuesday to vote PERIOD

I was kind of expecting this place to be a little bit more crowded said Michael Chen senior in LAS PERIOD But given the weather today I feel like this was more expected. despite the cold rainy weather University students still wanted to participate in this onceinfouryears event PERIOD

I thought it would be a historic moment to vote on the voting day said Jaime Yuen junior in LAS PERIOD My roommates and I didnt know what to expect so we decided to go on the day.
title: Daniels Graduate Hall - The Daily Illini
name: University of Illinois Urbana Champaign
